# table = '<table class="article"><tr class="a-head"><td class="a-left"><span class="a-u-name"><a href="/nForum/user/query/drei">drei</a></span><span class="a-u-sex" ><samp title="男生哦 在线" class="ico-pos-online-man" ></samp></span></td><td><ul class="c"><li><samp class="ico-pos-reply"></samp><a href="/nForum/article/ChildEducation/post/2068197" class="a-post">回复</a></l<li><samp class="ico-pos-template"></samp><a href="/nForum/article/ChildEducation/tmpl?id=2068197" class="a-post">模版回复</li><li><samp class="ico-pos-forward"></samp><a href="/nForum/article/ChildEducation/ajax_forward/2068197.json" class="a-func-forward">转寄</a></li><li><samp class="ico-pos-forward"></samp><a href="/nForum/article/ChildEducation/ajax_docross/28197.json" class="a-func-docross">转载</a></li><li><samp class="ico-pos-friend"></samp><a href="/nForum/article/ChildEducaon/ajax_addfavor/2068197.json" class="a-addfavor">关注</a></li><li><samp class="ico-pos-search"></samp><a href="/nForum/s/ticle?b=ChildEducation&au=drei">搜索</a></li><li><samp class="ico-pos-user"></samp><a href="/nForum/article/ChildEducation068197?au=drei">只看此ID</a></li></ul><span class="a-pos">楼主</span></td></tr><tr class="a-body"><td class="a-left"><div ="a-u-img"><img src="//static.mysmth.net/nForum/uploadFace/D/drei.8922.jpg" width="120px" height="120px" /></div><div class="a-u-uid">娃帅妈美</div><dl class="a-u-info"><dt>身份</dt><dd>用户</dd><dt>文章</dt><dd>33604</dd><dt>星座</dt><dd>双鱼座t><dd>19681</dd><dt>等级</dt><dd>紫檀(11)</dd></dl></td><td class="a-content"><p >发信人: drei (娃帅妈美), 信区: ChildEduc标&nbsp;&nbsp;题: 求助 小学一年级孩子遭遇校园霸凌 <br /> 发信站: 水木社区 (Thu Oct 13 23:46:34 2022), 站内 <br />&nbsp;&nb同学在足球课的时候踢伤下面。我娃属于那种被打了不敢还手的娃儿。之前还手时被老师批评，从此不再敢还手。体育课。 <br /> 我娃没对方用膝盖骨踢伤下面了……这点打人的孩子也认可，那个男孩儿经常在学校打我娃儿，尤其在教室或者楼道，我之前和那孩子妈妈微信沟通短2天后，就在体育课被他踢伤了下面，那孩子爸爸非常蛮横无理，北京市属国企的基层领导（轨道交通行业）和班主任说话都颐指气使的，大呼小叫，还说他家孩子打人都是一个巴掌拍不响……求助该怎么办。 <br /> 校长明确说换班不可能！没有先例，道歉也不能强迫，他们要班主任老师大呼小叫像命令佣人的口气。求助大家，我现在该怎么办？ <br /> -- <br /> <font class="f006">※ 修改:·drei 于 Oct 14 156.*]</font><font class="f000"> <br /> </font><font class="f000"></font><font class="f007">※ 来源:·水木社区 <a target="_bhref="http://m.mysmth.net">http://m.mysmth.net</a>·[FROM: 223.104.38.*]</font><font class="f000"> <br /> </font><div class="likes"><div class="like_name">有26位用户评价了这篇文章：</div><div class="like_list"><ul><li><span class="like_score_2">span class="like_user">zhaoyifan222:</span><span class="like_msg">继续报警，记入那孩子档案，伴随一生，以后考公出国都受影响me">(2022-10-14 07:25)</span></li><li><span class="like_score_0">[&nbsp;&nbsp;]</span><span class="like_user">haove:</span><span class="like_msg">光脚的还怕穿鞋的？去他爸爸单位告状</span><span class="like_time">(2022-10-14 08:47)</span></li><li><span class="like_score_0">[&nbsp;&nbsp;]</span><span class="like_user">vobt:</span><span class="like_msg">你们必须给你们主任和学校施加压力</span><span class="like_time">(2022-10-14 08:52)</span></li><li><span class="like_score_0">[&nbsp;&nbsp<span class="like_user">majia1988:</span><span class="like_msg">12345你值得拥有，学校小鞋都给你穿上了你害怕个啥。</span><s(2022-10-14 08:56)</span></li><li><span class="like_score_0">[&nbsp;&nbsp;]</span><span class="like_user">janex:</span><span class="like_msg">先训练自己孩子懂反抗，其次怂恿那个孩子继续祸害，引起群愤</span><span class="like_time">(2022-10-14 09:ss="like_score_0">[&nbsp;&nbsp;]</span><span class="like_user">xilong:</span><span class="like_msg">准备转学吧，然后12345、方投诉。</span><span class="like_time">(2022-10-14 09:15)</span></li><li><span class="like_score_1">[+5]</span><span class="like_user">h819:</span><span class="like_msg">细看 177 楼</span><span class="like_time">(2022-10-14 09:20)</span></li><lspan class="like_score_0">[&nbsp;&nbsp;]</span><span class="like_user">fattora:</span><span class="like_msg">记得lz这个id在着呢，现实里这么怂么</span><span class="like_time">(2022-10-14 09:29)</span></li><li><span class="like_score_0">[&nbsp;&nb><span class="like_user">danssion:</span><span class="like_msg">楼上有意思哈。另外，北京市属国企的基层领导好搞他啊</span><022-10-14 09:33)</span></li><li><span class="like_score_0">[&nbsp;&nbsp;]</span><span class="like_user">jxboylj:</span><span class="like_msg">报警，去教委，得留证据</span><span class="like_time">(2022-10-14 09:42)</span></li><li><span class="li>[&nbsp;&nbsp;]</span><span class="like_user">smily1126:</span><span class="like_msg">让你儿子打回去！校长说了换班不可能，先例，道歉不强迫</span><span class="like_time">(2022-10-14 09:46)</span></li><li><span class="like_score_0">[&nbsp;&nbsp;]span class="like_user">pigpang:</span><span class="like_msg">报警。同时找高年级小哥哥找这个孩子聊聊？聊聊别动手我感觉聊聊<(2022-10-14 09:54)</span></li><li><span class="like_score_0">[&nbsp;&nbsp;]</span><span class="like_user">Donaldcuc:</span><span class="like_msg">报警，留证据，去教委，到校长那里展示证据。去对方爸爸单位反应</span><span class="like_time">(2022-1an class="like_score_2">[-5]</span><span class="like_user">netherlands:</span><span class="like_msg">看半天觉得都是你一面之你没说</span><span class="like_time">(2022-10-14 10:17)</span></li><li><span class="like_score_2">[-5]</span><span class="e_user">xwzbupt:</span><span class="like_msg">一楼是不是没报过警，这种情况jc都不搭理的。还计入档案？呵呵</span><span classe">(2022-10-14 10:22)</span></li><li><span class="like_score_0">[&nbsp;&nbsp;]</span><span class="like_user">pebble001:</span><span class="like_msg">打教委电话投诉，教委会把校长训成孙子</span><span class="like_time">(2022-10-14 10:39)</span></l"like_score_0">[&nbsp;&nbsp;]</span><span class="like_user">Nakupenda:</span><span class="like_msg">投诉教育局，最近对校园><span class="like_time">(2022-10-14 10:42)</span></li><li><span class="like_score_0">[&nbsp;&nbsp;]</span><span class="like_user">lamtop:</span><span class="like_msg">国企央企最怕闹了，3天两头去他单位闹，贴大字报</span><span class="like_time">an></li><li><span class="like_score_1">[+3]</span><span class="like_user">renice:</span><span class="like_msg">什么叫一个巴日本南京大屠杀难道南京人活该？</span><span class="like_time">(2022-10-14 11:30)</span></li><li><span class="like_score_0">[&nbsp;&nbsp;]</span><span class="like_user">qweraz:</span><span class="like_msg">打回去</span><span class="like_time">(2010-14 12:02)</span></li><li><span class="like_score_1">[+3]</span><span class="like_user">zai:</span><span class="like_msg">媒体，找不着主流的就自媒体，霸凌、国企、学校不作为，多少爆点</span><span class="like_time">(2022-10-14 12:37)</span></li">[&nbsp;&nbsp;]</span><span class="like_user">oakruning:</span><span class="like_msg">媒体曝光</span><span class="like_ti(2022-10-14 12:52)</span></li><li><span class="like_score_0">[&nbsp;&nbsp;]</span><span class="like_user">upeachday:</span><span class="like_msg">你这不是孩子老实，是家长怂，国企基层领导算个屁啊</span><span class="like_time">(2022-10-14 13:02)<ss="like_score_1">[+5]</span><span class="like_user">yuan20111:</span><span class="like_msg">直接吓唬他家娃，当着他娃面摔他娃东西，狠起来</span><span class="like_time">(2022-10-14 13:15)</span></li><li><span class="like_score_0">[&nbsp;&nbsp;]</pan class="like_user">lily1234:</span><span class="like_msg">借这个帖还不敢公开学校名字？太怂</span><span class="like_time:18)</span></li><li><span class="like_score_0">[&nbsp;&nbsp;]</span><span class="like_user">tbywb:</span><span class="like_msg">公开是哪个学校，其他人好避坑</span><span class="like_time">(2022-10-14 13:33)</span></li></ul></div></div></p><!--<d-align:center;padding: 10px; margin:10px; font-size: 16px;"><a href="https://exp.newsmth.net/nforum/article/ChildEducation/2068197" target="_blank">体验模式阅读文章</a></div>--></td></tr><tr class="a-bottom"><td class="a-left"><ul class="a-funcinfo"><li><samp class="ico-pos-query"></samp><a href="/nForum/user/query/drei">查看</a></li><li><samp class="ico-pos-mess"/samp><a href="/nForum/mail/ChildEducation/reply/2068197?id=drei" class="a-post">发信</a></li><li><samp class="ico-pos-frid"></samp><a href="/nForum/friend/ajax_add.json?id=drei" class="a-func-friend a-post">加好友</a></li></ul></td><td><a href" class="c63f a-back">返回顶部</a></td></tr></table>'
